 <title>AAAI Conference on Weblogs and Social Media</title>
 <link>http://transmissionproject.org/events/2010/05/aaai-conference-on-weblogs-and-social-media</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;The International Conference on Weblogs and Social Media is a unique venue that brings together researchers from the disciplines of &lt;span class=&quot;caps&quot;&gt;NLP&lt;/span&gt;, Social Psychology, Data Mining, Sociology and Visualization to increase our understanding of social media in all its incarnations. Research that blends social science and technology is especially&amp;nbsp;encouraged.&lt;/p&gt;
